The idea here is as follows:
Consider the array : [1 , 2 , 3 , 4, 5 ,6 ,7 ] and k = 3;
First let us reverse the whole array : [ 7 , 6 , 5, 4 ,3 ,2 ,1 ]
Next, we reverse the elements from 0 to k - 1 : [ 5 , 6 , 7, 4 , 3 ,2 ,1]
Next we reverse the elements from k till the end : [ 5 , 6 ,7, 1, 2 , 3, 4]
